A vintage 1920s ballroom scene with three elegant dancers in Art Deco attire performing an intricate tango together, their movements creating flowing ribbons of gold, silver, and bronze that interweave between them in complex patterns. The dancers represent the three-way exchange of OAuth - one in deep burgundy representing the user, one in midnight blue representing the identity provider, and one in emerald green representing the application. The ribbons connecting them form a beautiful choreographed pattern suggesting data flowing back and forth. Warm amber lighting from crystal chandeliers casts dramatic shadows across a polished marble floor with geometric patterns. The scene has a sepia-toned warmth with rich jewel tones, ornate gilded frames on the walls, and the sophisticated atmosphere of a 1920s speakeasy. The composition emphasizes the graceful coordination and trust required between all three dancers to complete their elaborate routine.
